Why is it so hard to launch a Mac instance on Amazon e2?
text:
Why is it so hard to launch a mac instance on amazon e2?

I have been struggling with this for days. It's 10x harder than windows. Every single imaginable error possible.

It says "Launch initiation Failed"

All the guides are obsolete.

The official amazon tutorial hasn't even been updated to account for the new interface.

It will not even explain the source of the error. Only that the initiation failed.

Show HN: M3o.org: A Mastodon server for remote developers
text:
Hey all

Just sharing this new Mastodon server I started for remote developers. Personally I've been hacking solo and on open source for 7 years. More recently with a team but we were fully remote because of COVID. I feel like there's not really a good community around that and the emergence of Mastodon recently made me think there's an opportunity to create one.

Join us if you're a remote developers https://M3O.org
